title: Acting Challenges + RHONJ & RHOC!

description:
Danny starts off the show with an acting detour, then dives into this week's The Real Housewives of New Jersey, which featured Marge Sr.'s birthday and Tre packing up her sausage makers. After Jersey, Danny dips into The Real Housewives of Orange County, where the altitude is getting to the gals.


RHONJ: 9:00ish

RHOC: 32:00ish
